# ============================================================
# Sanity CMS — required untuk /blog integration
# ============================================================
# Signup di https://sanity.io, buat project baru, lalu isi:

NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id-here
NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_DATASET=production
NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_API_VERSION=2024-12-01

# Optional: untuk draft mode / preview (dashboard Sanity → API → Tokens)
# SANITY_API_READ_TOKEN=your-read-token-here

# ============================================================
# Cara setup:
#
# 1. Signup di https://sanity.io/login → buat project baru
# 2. Copy project ID dari sanity.io/manage → taruh di NEXT_PUBLIC_SANITY_PROJECT_ID
# 3. Copy file ini jadi .env.local (tanpa .example)
# 4. Restart dev server: npm run dev
#
# Untuk mengelola konten (Studio):
#
# Option A — Hosted studio (recommended):
#   - Buka https://<your-project-id>.sanity.studio setelah deploy
#   - Deploy: cd . && npx sanity deploy (di direktori ini, pakai sanity.config.ts)
#
# Option B — Standalone local studio:
#   - npx sanity dev  → buka http://localhost:3333
#   - (menggunakan sanity.config.ts di root)
#
# Embedded studio di Next.js sementara di-skip karena React 19 compat issue.
# ============================================================
